Sample Data: A Latent Variable Structural Model With an Influential Case

Source: R/data.R
sem_dat2.Rd

A ten-variable dataset with 200 cases, with one influential case.

Usage

sem_dat2

Format

A data frame with 200 rows and 10 variables:

case_id

Case ID. Character.

x1

Indicator. Numeric.

x2

Indicator. Numeric.

x3

Indicator. Numeric.

x4

Indicator. Numeric.

x5

Indicator. Numeric.

x6

Indicator. Numeric.

x7

Indicator. Numeric.

x8

Indicator. Numeric.

x9

Indicator. Numeric.

Examples

library(lavaan)
data(sem_dat2)
mod <-
"
f1 =~  x1 + x2 + x3
f2 =~  x4 + x5 + x6
f3 =~  x7 + x8 + x9
f2 ~ a * f1
f3 ~ b * f2
ab := a * b
"
fit <- sem(mod, sem_dat2)
summary(fit)
